These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, almond-milk, water, cola, iced-tea, lemonade
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, indonesian, polish, colombian, turkish, canadian, spanish
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, lacrosse, climbing, tennis, water-polo, weightlifting
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, motorbike, car, skateboard, roller, scooter
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is the colombian##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the indonesian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the russian is on the right of the spanish##1
 6. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the turkish##1
 8. the person driving the car is between the person driving the scooter and the canadian##2
 9. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking cola##1
12. the person drinking cola is the person driving the taxi##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the polish##1
14. the canadian is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the person driving the roller is on the left of the spanish##1
16. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
17. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the polish##1
18. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the turkish##1
19. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | milk  | iced-tea        | cola | almond-milk      | water     | mirinda      | lemonade     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | colombian         | spanish   | russian | canadian    | turkish | polish |
| Sport         | lacrosse | tennis | badminton | rowing | weightlifting  | water-polo  | climbing    |
| Transport     | skateboard  | roller         | taxi     | snowmobile    | motorbike | car     | scooter     |

